---

<MainLayout
  title="Our Services | Custom Cabinets, Kitchen Remodeling & Built-Ins | Murrieta CA"
  description="Explore First Class WoodWorks' custom cabinetry services in Murrieta, CA. Kitchen cabinets, bathroom vanities, entertainment centers, fireplace surrounds & closet built-ins — 100% in-house. Call (951) 973-1265."
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />

  <article class="pt-24 pb-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

      <nav class="text-xs text-zinc-400 mb-4 reveal" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-yellow-600 transition">Home</a></li>
          <li class="text-zinc-300">/</li>
          <li class="text-zinc-600 font-bold">Our Services</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>

      <header class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-10 reveal">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
          Our <span class="text-yellow-600 italic">Services</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-400">
          <span class="text-yellow-600">Murrieta, California</span>
          <span class="hidden md:block text-zinc-200">&bull;</span>
          <span>100% In-House Craftsmanship</span>
          <span class="hidden md:block text-zinc-200">&bull;</span>
          <span class="text-zinc-500">Licensed &amp; Bonded</span>
        </div>
        <div class="h-px w-24 bg-yellow-600/30 mx-auto mt-6"></div>
      </header>

      <div class="services-intro max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-10 reveal">
        <p class="text-lg text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed italic">
          First Class WoodWorks builds every cabinet, vanity, and built-in by hand in our Murrieta shop. No subcontractors, no particle board, no flat-packs. From custom kitchens to fireplace surrounds, each project features furniture-grade plywood, dovetail joinery, and Blum soft-close hardware backed by a lifetime warranty.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 mb-24 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-14">

          <!-- Service 1: Custom Kitchen Cabinets -->
          <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center reveal">
            <div class="relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-video">
              <Image src={kitchenImage} alt="Custom kitchen cabinets built by First Class WoodWorks in Murrieta CA" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Custom Kitchen Cabinets</h2>
              <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                The kitchen is the heart of your home, and big-box cabinets in standard 3-inch increments waste space with filler strips. Our <a href="/services/cabinet-maker" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">cabinet maker</a> team builds to the 1/16th of an inch, maximizing every square inch of storage.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> Blum soft-close hardware (lifetime warranty)</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> $500 – $1,200+ per linear foot</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/services/custom-kitchen-cabinets" class="inline-block bg-zinc-900 text-white px-6 py-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-yellow-600 transition">
                Learn More
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Service 2: Kitchen Remodeling -->
          <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center reveal">
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Kitchen Remodeling</h2>
              <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Full gut remodels that transform outdated kitchens into high-value showpieces. We handle the cabinetry, countertop coordination, and finish carpentry while engineering the work triangle for maximum efficiency in your Murrieta or <a href="/cities/temecula" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">Temecula</a> home.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> 3D renderings before any work begins</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> 8–12 week turnaround</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/services/kitchen-remodeling" class="inline-block bg-zinc-900 text-white px-6 py-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-yellow-600 transition">
                Learn More
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1 md:order-2 relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-video">
              <Image src={kitchenImage} alt="Kitchen remodeling project in Murrieta by First Class WoodWorks" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Service 3: Bathroom Vanities -->
          <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center reveal">
            <div class="relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-video">
              <Image src={bathroomImage} alt="Custom bathroom vanity with furniture-grade plywood in Murrieta CA" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Bathroom Vanities & Storage</h2>
              <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Custom vanities built to the exact width of your walls, eliminating the gaps where dust and moisture collect. Every vanity is sealed with post-catalyzed conversion varnish for decades of humidity resistance in master suites and guest baths alike.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> Moisture-resistant conversion varnish finish</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> $400 – $3,000 per vanity unit</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/services/bathroom-remodeling" class="inline-block bg-zinc-900 text-white px-6 py-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-yellow-600 transition">
                Learn More
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Service 4: Entertainment Centers & Built-Ins -->
          <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center reveal">
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Entertainment Centers & Built-Ins</h2>
              <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Turn empty niches and bare walls into stunning focal points. We specialize in seamless built-in cabinetry that looks original to your home's architecture — from floating media consoles to full wall libraries with integrated lighting.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> Concealed wiring &amp; custom TV sizing</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> Starting at $1,200 — large units $11,000+</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1 md:order-2 relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-video">
              <Image src={builtinImage} alt="Custom entertainment center built-in by First Class WoodWorks Murrieta" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Service 5: Fireplace Mantels & Surrounds -->
          <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center reveal">
            <div class="relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-video">
              <Image src={fireplaceImage} alt="Handcrafted custom fireplace mantel and surround in Murrieta CA" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Fireplace Mantels & Surrounds</h2>
              <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                A custom mantel anchors any living room. We craft solid wood mantels, shiplap surrounds, and floor-to-ceiling fireplace build-outs — matching your existing trim or creating an entirely new style, from rustic reclaimed to clean shaker lines.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> Matched to existing cabinetry &amp; trim</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> See our <a href="/projects/bear-creek-remodel" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">Bear Creek project</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Service 6: Custom Closet Built-Ins -->
          <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center reveal">
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Custom Closet Built-Ins</h2>
              <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Premium walk-in closet systems built from the same furniture-grade materials as our kitchen cabinets. No particle board, no wire shelving. Dovetail drawer boxes, adjustable shelving, and integrated lighting designed for luxury <a href="/cities/murrieta" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">Murrieta</a> master suites.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> Furniture-grade plywood &amp; solid hardwoods</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> Zero particle board or wire racks</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/services/custom-closet-built-ins" class="inline-block bg-zinc-900 text-white px-6 py-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-yellow-600 transition">
                Learn More
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1 md:order-2 relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-video">
              <Image src={closetImage} alt="Custom closet built-in with furniture-grade plywood by First Class WoodWorks Murrieta" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Comparison Table -->
          <section class="bg-zinc-50 p-8 rounded-sm border border-zinc-100 reveal">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 text-center">Custom vs. Big-Box — Why It Matters</h2>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm text-left">
                <thead class="border-b border-zinc-200">
                  <tr>
                    <th class="pb-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-600">Feature</th>
                    <th class="pb-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400">Big-Box / Pre-Fab</th>
                    <th class="pb-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-yellow-600">First Class WoodWorks</th>
                  </tr>
