                <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200">
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Materials</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Particle board / Melamine</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Furniture-grade plywood & hardwoods</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Sizing</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Standard 3" increments (fillers)</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Built to the 1/16th inch</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Hardware</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Basic plastic / metal mix</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Blum soft-close (lifetime warranty)</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Joinery</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Staples & cam locks</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Dovetail & mortise-and-tenon</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Finish</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Vinyl wrap or spray paint</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Post-catalyzed conversion varnish</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Longevity</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">5–10 years</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Lifetime (heirloom quality)</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">ROI</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Low (generic look)</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">High (increases home appraisal)</td></tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Pro Tip -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-600 p-8 reveal">
            <h4 class="text-zinc-900 font-bold mb-2">Cabinet Builder Pro-Tip:</h4>
            <p class="italic text-zinc-600">"Cheap cabinets fail in Southern California's climate. Triple-digit Inland Empire summers cause particle board to swell, delaminate, and release formaldehyde. Furniture-grade plywood with a conversion varnish seal is the only material that performs for a lifetime in Murrieta, Temecula, and the surrounding valley."</p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-8 sticky top-32">
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 text-white p-10 rounded-sm">
            <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-2xl mb-2 text-yellow-600">Start Your Project</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] font-bold mb-6">Murrieta, CA &bull; 5.0 Star Rated</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/80 text-sm mb-8">
              <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-3">Licensed, Bonded & Insured</li>
              <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-3">A+ BBB Accredited</li>
              <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-3">100% In-House — No Subcontractors</li>
              <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-3">Blum Lifetime-Warranty Hardware</li>
              <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-3">Free 3D Design Renderings</li>
              <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-3">HEPA Dust Extraction On-Site</li>
              <li>8–12 Weeks Design to Install</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="tel:9519731265" class="block text-center border border-yellow-600 py-4 font-bold hover:bg-yellow-600 hover:text-zinc-900 transition mb-3 tracking-wider">
              {phone}
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-yellow-600 text-zinc-900 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-yellow-700 transition">
              Get a Free Quote
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-zinc-50 border border-zinc-200 p-8 rounded-sm reveal">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500 mb-6">Our Services</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-600">
              <li><a href="/services/cabinet-maker" class="hover:text-yellow-600 transition font-bold">Cabinet Maker</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/custom-kitchen-cabinets" class="hover:text-yellow-600 transition font-bold">Custom Kitchen Cabinets</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/kitchen-remodeling" class="hover:text-yellow-600 transition font-bold">Kitchen Remodeling</a></li>
